<a href="#Day1"><h2>Day1:Coimbatore - Madurai - Kodaikanal</h2></a>
<p>On reaching Coimbatore/Madurai airport/railway station, meet our ihpl representative who will help you take a transfer to this beautiful destination, Kodaikanal. Check-in to the hotel on arriving Kodaikanal. Take rest and enjoy the evening at leisure. Have a comfortable overnight stay at the hotel.
</p>
